            <h3>Choosing the power Supply</h3>
            <p>Most of the time, in assembling a personal computer, one of the most important aspects of a computer system, the power supply, is ignored.</p>
            <p><b>The power supply</b> is the component without which the computer cannot start and run. Whether the computer is used for office or gaming, it requires a power supply with a large enough capacity </p>
            <p>pentru a mentine functionabilitatea, intr-un mod corespunzator, a tuturor componetntelor.</p>
            <p>When it comes to manufacturers, there is a wide range of brands, such as Aqirys, Cooler Master, Lian Li, Seasonic, nJoy, Corsair, Zalman.
            <p>For an office computer a maximum of 450W is recommended, while gaming systems require at least 500W real power (minimum Bronze Certificate).</p>
